        "heading": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Efemera was created to capture the quiet, fleeting moments that shape our lives.",
            "heading_tag": "h2",
            "heading_font_class": "fs-heading-1-base"
          }
        },
        "text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>A laugh, a glance that lingers, a familiar scent, a gentle touch — moments that pass in an instant yet leave lasting impressions on the heart.</p><p>The name itself comes from <em>ephemeral</em> — a reminder that the most meaningful things in life are often the most transient. We believe the adornments you wear become quiet witnesses to those memories, letting the joy of past moments sparkle again whenever you see them.</p>",
            "text_font_class": "fs-body-100"
          }
        },
