        },
        "subheading": {
          "type": "subheading",
          "settings": {
            "subheading": "<p>SoHo cobblestones. Cast-iron galleries. The energy of a city that never stops making.</p>",
            "subheading_font_class": "fs-heading-5-base"
          }
        },
        "text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Every Efemera piece is handcrafted in New York City. Each begins as hand-carved wax, cast in molten 14k gold using lost-wax casting — the same technique goldsmiths have used since 3000 BCE. Then filed, sanded through progressively finer grits, and polished by hand at the bench.</p><p>Nothing sits in inventory. Each piece is made to order, crafted specifically for you. This means a 3–4 week production time, but it also means your piece carries the intention and care of being made just for this moment in your life.</p>",
            "text_font_class": "fs-body-100"
          }
        },
