            "focal_point": "image_presentation",
            "title": "14k Yellow Gold",
            "text": "<p>58.3% pure gold alloyed with copper and silver. Harder than 18k, so delicate organic tendrils survive daily wear. The alloy flows better when molten, filling the finest sculptural details. A warm buttery tone that looks like it grew rather than was manufactured.</p>"
