            "title": "Freshwater Pearls",
            "text": "<p>Solid nacre all the way through. Thousands of microscopic aragonite layers create luster through the same physics that makes the sky blue. No two pearls reflect light identically. We choose baroque shapes because they belong in nature, not a display case.</p>"
